\par \hich\af0\dbch\af4\loch\f0 This document has been prepared to explain the timing and applications of cards and their effects in ON THE EDGE. The intention is to provide a few simple and understandable schemes which can reso\hich\af0\dbch\af4\loch\f0 
lve some of the more obscure and vexing rules questions that sometimes arise. Readers should be aware that the issues detailed in this document are meant to address rules questions which have arisen slowly over the months since ON THE EDGE was released in
\hich\af0\dbch\af4\loch\f0  \hich\af0\dbch\af4\loch\f0 
1994; many players may find the discussions below unnecessary for conducting their normal game play. As always, members of the ON THE EDGE community are encouraged to play the game -- their game -- in the fashion that they find most enjoyable; if you find
\hich\af0\dbch\af4\loch\f0  \hich\af0\dbch\af4\loch\f0 the material here too abstract or erudite, or just plain confusing, just blame me, feel free to ignore this document, and have fun the way you know best how to! With those provisions out of the way.. 

